    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Awed__ by the___ beau----ty_____ of__ thy__ vir--gin-------i-ty___ and the re---splend----en---cy_____ of__ thy__ great__ pu-------ri-ty,___ the an--gel Ga---bri-el__ called___ out__ to thee_____ thus,___ O The--o--to-----kos:__ What____ wor-thy___ hymn____ of___ praise_____ can I of----fer__ un-------to thee?___ How__ shall I re---fer__ to____ thee?__ I am caught____ in be--wil--er--ment.__ Where-fore,__ as__ com-mand---ed,___ I cry___ out: Maid------en full__ of grace,___ re-joice___ thou._______"
    }
